{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_01_02",
  "title": "井川葵 2話 趣味は何？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "女子高生A",
      "speakerNameEn": "High",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あーっ！　あんた、井川葵じゃん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow! You’re Aoi Igawa-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "女子高生A",
      "speakerNameEn": "High",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "案外小っちゃいんだ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re smaller than I expected!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.7998116126427286,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 5.86666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（十メートルほど前に偶然にも井川葵がいた）\n（ガラの悪そうな女の子達に囲まれている）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I happen to see Aoi Igawa about a dozen meters ahead.)\n(She’s surrounded by some mean-looking girls.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.64069692177501,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 12.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "おい、君達、何をしてる！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey! You there. What are you doing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-multi-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4199.999999999999,
          "startTime": 17
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 15.2666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　君は……\nあ、君達――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? I know you…\nHey‚ girls――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 19.8333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "逃げていったか……怪我はしてないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew‚ they ran off. Did they hurt you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.833333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 23.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "どうして、僕が怪我をするの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why would they hurt me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "だって今、不良っぽい子達に絡まれてたろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Those girls looked like trouble.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 29.0333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "酷いな、さっきのは僕のファンだよ\n握手してって言ってきただけさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t be mean. They were my fans.\nThey just wanted a handshake.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.43333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "僕のファンが二人も減ったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You just cost me two fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 36.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "あ～あ、なんてことをしてくれるんだよ、君は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah~ah. Are you going to take responsibility for this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "いや、たぶん彼女達は\n君のこと嫌いにはならないんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look‚ I doubt they’ll blame you\nfor what just happened.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 45.7333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "僕は言い訳とこんにゃくは嫌いなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I hate excuses as much as I hate konjac.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "悪かったよ、ごめん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right. I’m sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "言葉だけの謝罪なんて一ミリの価値もないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyone can apologize by moving their mouth.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 50.3666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 53.4333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "分かった\nどうすればいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay then.\nHow can I earn your forgiveness?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 56.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、体で返して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By your body‚ of course.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 59.2999999523163
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 59.2999999523163
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――一時間後　アンティークショップ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few hours later‚ at an antique shop",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、このテーブルは大きくて頑丈そうでいいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ this table looks big and sturdy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 66.8333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "兄さん達が来たら、沢山皿を並べられる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I could fit all my brothers around this easily.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "カップル女性",
      "speakerNameEn": "Couple‚",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ねえ、あれ、井川葵じゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ isn’t that Aoi Igawa?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 70.0666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "カップル男性",
      "speakerNameEn": "Couple‚",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "えっ、でも男連れてるぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh‚ but she’s got a guy with her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "カップル男性",
      "speakerNameEn": "Couple‚",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "人違いじゃね？　超似てるけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Probably just a lookalike――does really look like her‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 78.7333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "マズい。この状況はとてもマズいぞ\nなあ、早く決めてくれないかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is bad. Yep‚ this is real bad.\nHey‚ can we hurry up here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 85.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "荷物持ちくん、僕を急かさないでくれよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re here to carry my stuff. Don’t rush the process.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "ゆっくり選ばせて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let me take my time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 90.5333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "このままだとゴシップ記事が\n週刊誌に載りかねない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ll be in every gossip column\nin every rag across the city tomorrow!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "僕達は別にやましいことはしていないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re not doing anything wrong.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "そうだけど、君に迷惑は掛けたくない\nせめて手だけでも離してくれ",
      "translations": {
